  • Packages that use edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem 
    Package Description
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem
    Manage local files and directories that represent computational chemistry experiments
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.amber
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the AMBER software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.charmm
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the CHARMM software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.common
    Manage common chemical file formats.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.gamess
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the GAMESS software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.gaussian
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the Gaussian software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.gromacs
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the GROMACS software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.namd
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the NAMD software package.
    edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.nwchem
    Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the NWChem software package.
